 ('9', '9', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The LAB PropShop\",\"slug\":\"the-lab-propshop\",\"postDate\":1465876534,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"14\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>It\\u2019s important that every picture is one of a kind and 100% YOU. The LAB\\u2019s PropShop is fully loaded with tons of different accessories, masks and other knick-knacks necessary to make each picture anything but ordinary. Having an 80\\u2019s party and need a rockin\\u2019 mullet wig? We can cater the PropShop to match any party theme at an additional charge.<\\/p>\"}}', '2016-06-14 03:55:34', '2016-06-14 03:55:34', 'b8fc4e59-43b6-4952-a698-962d63e50723'),
